{"tid":1236493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"圍自己友不如圍敵人","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:29:20.000Z","uid":263306,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31cbff32ba6c99d489685ebfe45dcda01c44d1ff","tid":1236493,"uid":263306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"今日龍和道啲人挑起話民主派議員做唔到野，我聽到好唔開心，話晒大家都係自己人，無功都有勞，點解硬要人跟你哋的決定做事呢？<br />\n<br />\n朱迪叫大家諗下野，無錯，呢個時候是要發揮創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要圍自己友，點解唔去圍建制呀？之前大家話要比壓力佢哋，都無做到。<br />\n<br />\n還有以子之茅攻子之盾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係諗下，如果葉劉咁想做特首，我們比個機會佢拉林鄭下台，你又話得唔得呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73156a33b9406a144a1ea9b3a8bda6be0a4506bb","tid":1236493,"uid":149751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:25:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9b615fc6890733f31036bbdcdcdbcf51a4f9d6c","tid":1236493,"uid":149751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:25:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3f22b0c26f56723dcaf88cfbf4ebf2144dc6922","tid":1236493,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:27:02.000Z","msg":"新AC"},{"pid":"ebf435885d6499d96d2d1df85b9ba83a82a353a0","tid":1236493,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3f22b0c26f56723dcaf88cfbf4ebf2144dc6922","tid":1236493,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:27:02.000Z","msg":"新AC"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:27:13.000Z","msg":"又想叫人衝"},{"pid":"9382c0409d705791dec79d24c2bc91f0